{"tid":587822,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"拉莫斯為大解離場5分鐘","createTime":"2018-03-10T17:17:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-13T02:31:43.000Z","uid":58022,"like":434,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":112,"replies":[{"pid":"1546dbcd881a419b297216a95f6c7ed97c1f7e5e","tid":587822,"uid":58022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T17:17:21.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=f523n4gChKvkFqIVfjeVmozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=a93d7483\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】周六西甲早場，皇家馬德里中堅沙治奧拉莫斯在下半場突然自動離場，於5分鐘後回來，到底是為甚麼？<br />\n<br />\n皇家馬德里鬥主場的伊巴，在84分鐘憑球王基斯坦奴朗拿度頂入，個人梅開二度，以2:1絕殺成功。賽事有段小插曲，隊長沙治奧拉莫斯（Sergio Ramos）於73分鐘兩軍仍踢成1:1時，突然自動離場，在5分鐘後才回來。<br />\n<br />\n教練施丹賽後表示，拉莫斯離場不是因為受傷：「他忍不住要去大便。」由於當時皇馬已用盡3個換人名額，因此拉莫斯未能被換走，但又實在忍不住，所以只好回到更衣室解決，令皇馬有5分鐘時間只得10人應戰，幸好仍能獲得最後勝利。<br />\n<br />\n皇馬今戰全取3分後，穩坐西甲第3位，施丹說：「這場勝利令我有特別的感覺，因為伊巴是一支很好的球隊，而且踢得出色。他們的主場很難踢，我們早知道要吃點苦，我們遇上困難，但以自身的性格去戰鬥到底，最終獲得勝利。」<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : &copy;AFP<br />\n<br />\n隊長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa9b5b65db4621bc96ba1d235327fbd93b13a936","tid":587822,"uid":136901,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T17:18:36.000Z","msg":"拉膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1833c51af312539dc3fdfab730c879608e8547c","tid":587822,"uid":5843,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T17:18:53.000Z","msg":"笑死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51b6b273bec709a63afa6630ece5052a251ce8de","tid":587822,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T17:19:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ff9c506e98d6a30857fe10ec34ba5991584a412","tid":587822,"uid":9581,"like":1,